    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/1e52f705f17f60d0c26b7696fab4dc93.poster.avif?t=1758301190\" width=800 height=46 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/1e52f705f17f60d0c26b7696fab4dc93.webm?t=1758301190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/1e52f705f17f60d0c26b7696fab4dc93.mp4?t=1758301190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/4da09dc819016282890222775b626ca3.avif?t=1758301190\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pixelart Character Creator!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring your game projects to life with Pixelart Character Creator! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you’re developing a top-down RPG, an adventurous farming simulator, or any other 2D game, our tool is here to help you create unique character sprites with ease. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/f86c5f1dd2d34c76d9736bda1b754a16.poster.avif?t=1758301190\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/f86c5f1dd2d34c76d9736bda1b754a16.webm?t=1758301190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/f86c5f1dd2d34c76d9736bda1b754a16.mp4?t=1758301190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Key Features:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Comprehensive Sprite Sheets: Generate character sprite sheets featuring 8 animations, including Walking, Idle, and various attack and farming actions. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expressive Faces: Complement your character sprites with matching face sprites, each offering 8 unique expressions to enhance storytelling and player engagement. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engine Compatibility: Export your sprites for use in any major game development engine, such as Game Maker, Unity, Godot, RPG Maker, and more. No matter your platform, our sprites integrate easily. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/7fb48dc5b139712784582eaf2057ebcc.poster.avif?t=1758301190\" width=800 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/7fb48dc5b139712784582eaf2057ebcc.webm?t=1758301190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/7fb48dc5b139712784582eaf2057ebcc.mp4?t=1758301190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Included Animations:</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Walking: Natural movements to traverse your game world. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Idle: Character stances that breathe life into moments of pause. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attack with Sword: Sword strikes to combat your enemies. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attack with Axe: Axe swings for gathering resources. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attack with Pickaxe: Mining actions for gathering resources. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Attack with Hoe: Perfect for farming games. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watering with Watercan: Essential for nurturing crops in farming games. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dead: Static dead sprite for impactful in-game consequences. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unleash your creativity and streamline your game development process with Pixelart Character Creator. Craft characters that resonate with your vision and captivate your audience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/942d3479b0ff6cf6585b1a1a0d427187.poster.avif?t=1758301190\" width=800 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/942d3479b0ff6cf6585b1a1a0d427187.webm?t=1758301190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/942d3479b0ff6cf6585b1a1a0d427187.mp4?t=1758301190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/1e52f705f17f60d0c26b7696fab4dc93.poster.avif?t=1758301190\" width=800 height=46 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/1e52f705f17f60d0c26b7696fab4dc93.webm?t=1758301190\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089670/extras/1e52f705f17f60d0c26b7696fab4dc93.mp4?t=1758301190\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
